    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Triacanthoneus toro n. gen., n. sp., paratype, ovigerous female (CL 3.4 mm) from Bocas del Toro, Caribbean coast of Panama, USNM 1145376: A, right (major) cheliped, lateral; B, same, carpus and chela, mesial; C, same, chela fingers; D, left (minor) cheliped, lateral; E, same, chela, mesial; F, second pereiopod, lateral; G, third pereiopod, lateral; H, same, dactylus; I, fifth pereiopod, lateral." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/198867/files/figure.png" ;
